add_strata              Adds strata for survival analysis to the
                        general_info data frame.
apply_filters           Manual data filtering ahead of plotting.
column_check            Called by preprocess_data to check that all
                        required columns are present in the provided
                        file.
create_chimerism_df     Creates a chimerism data frame based on
                        chimerism_raw and end_date_df, that contains
                        patno, chimerism, rel_chimerism_dat and
                        surface_marker columns.
create_end_date_df      Creates a gvhd data frame based on
                        general_info_raw and mrd_raw, that contains
                        patno, transpldt and rel_term_dat
create_gvhd_df          Creates a gvhd data frame based on gvhd_raw and
                        end_date_df, that contains gvhd events occuring
                        at and in between regular checkups.
create_ngs_df           Creates ngs data frame based on ngs_raw.
create_treatment_df     Creates treatment data frame based on dli and
                        aza data frames.
draw_chimerism_plot     Generate MRD + chimerism plot for a given
                        patient.
draw_clinical_course    Draw clinical course figures and export to PDF.
draw_clinical_course_chimerism
                        Draw clinical course figures and export to PDF.
draw_events_plot        Generate events plot for a given patient
draw_mrd_plot           Generate MRD plot for a given patient
draw_swimmerplot        Draw swimmer plot and export to PNG.
interval_finder         Called by the preprocess_data function to
                        identify immune suppression intervals, based on
                        the immune suppression data frame.
make_dummy_legend       Called by the draw_clinical_course function to
                        create GVHD dummy legends.
nmds_figures_main       Run analysis using the nmds_figures_main
                        function.
plot_chimerism_timeline
                        Generate MRD + Chimerism + GVHD timeline for a
                        given patient
plot_patient_timeline   Generate MRD + GVHD timeline for a given
                        patient
preprocess_data         Preprocess data ahead of manual filtering and
                        plotting and.
select_one_patient      Called by the draw_clinical_course function to
                        select one patient per graph.
standardize_drug        Called by the preprocess_data function to
                        standardize drug names in the immune
                        suppression data frame, based on a provided
                        mapping data frame.
swimmerplot             Called by draw_swimmerplot to draw swimmer
                        plot.
x_range_finder          Called by the draw_clinical_course function to
                        find the range of MRD x-axis values.
y_limit_finder          Called by the draw_clinical_course function to
                        find the upper limit of the MRD and/or
                        chimerism y-axis.
